{"tid":1427451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天琦有野同大家講","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:21:56.000Z","uid":21638,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4a8c1049a81c0012b0802e3227af405b79c707","tid":1427451,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d4yNCcS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd4yNCcS.jpg&h=f1184f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明有部份淺黃認為要集中反送中條例<br />\n我認同<br />\n但唔改變個政權制度跟本係做唔到5大訴求<br />\n希望大家認清事實真相<br />\n葉虎事件已經話比我地聽我地係同緊共產黨打杖<br />\n林奠係一個傳聲筒<br />\n佢無話事權<br />\n<br />\n對準目標，香港無得輸<br />\n一輸真係就陷家剷<br />\n無可能再發起第二次咁大型既社運<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c3a48f9bd92eeed1b3bf6d45f3ab3b9000d1357e","tid":1427451,"uid":53377,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localpresshk/videos/1788430144706792?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalpresshk%2Fvideos%2F1788430144706792%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=7c6a1043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localpresshk/videos/1788430144706792?sfns=mo</a> <br />\n<br />\n0425: 「當獨裁成為一個事實既時候，我哋仲有啲乜嘢可以做？革命就係我地既義務，依個係唯一既方法。」"},{"pid":"15074239ab98e0b5bf03f07a4c86538fe33c3f7f","tid":1427451,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"點解我地香港人咁聰明 亦都好多做緊天琦相同既野 但就點都諗唔到佢咁簡潔有力既口號 論點"},{"pid":"f606935c3f53429a5a329e13febd43e4d965e862","tid":1427451,"uid":21638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:21:56.000Z","msg":"香港人道德潔僻太重<br />\n叫佢地睇下烏克蘭自由之戰<br />\n人地火牆燒得幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}